item.title: Normal People: The complex terrain of modern relationships
item.description: Disclaimer: This is mostly a brain dump of how much I liked this series. So, if you are interested in me raving and blabbering about it, not to mention the generous spoilers, don’t read this. Also, it’s not one of my finest works. I just wanted to record everything I observed. Introduction Normal People is a 2020 12-episode romance web series based on a book by Sally Rooney produced by Hulu and BBC.
